                                    <b class="caret"></b></a><ul class="dropdown-menu dropdown-menu-large row"><li class="span3"><ul><li class="dropdown-header">Events</li><li class="divider"></li><li><a href="http://virtualglobetrotting.com/category/events/abandoned/">Abandoned</a></li><li><a href="http://virtualglobetrotting.com/category/events/vehicle-accidents/">Accidents</a></li><li><a href="http://virtualglobetrotting.com/category/events/in-the-news/">In The News</a></li><li><a href="http://virtualglobetrotting.com/category/events/military/">Military</a></li><li><a href="http://virtualglobetrotting.com/category/events/movie-locations/">Movie Locations</a></li><li><a href="http://virtualglobetrotting.com/category/events/murder-sites/">Murder Sites</a></li><li><a href="http://virtualglobetrotting.com/category/events/olympic-sites/">Olympic Sites</a></li><li><a href="http://virtualglobetrotting.com/category/events/tv-locations/">TV Locations</a></li><li class="dropdown-more"><a href="http://virtualglobetrotting.com/category/events/">More&hellip;</a></li><li class="dropdown-header">Land</li><li class="divider"></li><li><a href="http://virtualglobetrotting.com/category/land/artwork-sculpture/">Artwork - Sculpture</a></li><li><a href="http://virtualglobetrotting.com/category/land/artwork-land-art-geoglyphs/">Artwork - Land Art</a></li><li><a href="http://virtualglobetrotting.com/category/land/golf-courses/">Golf Courses</a></li><li><a href="http://virtualglobetrotting.com/category/land/mazes/">Mazes</a></li><li><a href="http://virtualglobetrotting.com/category/land/parks/">Parks</a></li><li><a href="http://virtualglobetrotting.com/category/land/pollution/">Pollution</a></li><li><a href="http://virtualglobetrotting.com/category/land/raceways-car/">Raceways</a></li><li><a href="http://virtualglobetrotting.com/category/land/zoos/">Zoos</a></li><li class="dropdown-more"><a href="http://virtualglobetrotting.com/category/land/">More&hellip;</a></li></ul></li><li class="sp